        <div id='title'>
          <p>I am an author, speaker, and loud-mouth on the design of enterprise software. This site contains lots of my writing on software development, which primarily focuses on software design and agile methods. I work for <a href='http://www.thoughtworks.com'>ThoughtWorks</a>, a software delivery and consulting company.</p>
