            <div class = 'newsEntry'>
            <h3><a href = 'http://martinfowler.com/bliki/MotionGraphics.html'>Bliki: MotionGraphics</a></h3>
            
            <p class = 'date'>Mon 29 Nov 2010 21:36</p>
            
            <div class = 'content'><p>As I've been using slides again as a visual channel in my talks,
              I've been making use of animation with diagrams to help communicate
              my points. The major presentation programs (Keynote and Powerpoint)
              have long supported animation, but I've been inclinded to look for
              motion grahics tools that are more powerful and easier to use.</p>
            <p class = 'more'><a href = 'http://martinfowler.com/bliki/MotionGraphics.html'>more...</a></p>
            </div>
            </div>
